  "detailed_description": "Fung Guys is an online-multiplayer, team-based, party game, heavily focused on exciting PvP minigames.<br>Enter an enchanted, stylized world in which you must win minigames to achieve the toad wizard’s approval.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885480/extras/6f8a4103bf47b41810b763e1f702d153.poster.avif?t=1654361325\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885480/extras/6f8a4103bf47b41810b763e1f702d153.webm?t=1654361325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885480/extras/6f8a4103bf47b41810b763e1f702d153.mp4?t=1654361325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885480/extras/c7f70ba4b7e09a61dcc19b1a914aed08.avif?t=1654361325\" width=489 height=158 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Iconic Minigames - Play through exciting minigames: Capture the Flag, Spleef, King of the Hill, and Falling Platform.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>PvP - Dash and bash your enemies and friends to victory.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online Multiplayer - Host public/private lobbies, or join public servers.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Whimsical Setting - Play through beautiful enchanted forest levels.</li></ul>",
